{"tid":1434363,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"短時間唔好塞交通 但地區性集會要繼續","createTime":"2019-08-08T18:05:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T10:10:58.000Z","uid":5378,"like":42,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"54da933d3047ae02f55e88d3798aebcf607728a7","tid":1434363,"uid":5378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:05:10.000Z","msg":"發覺身邊中立既真心好介意阻到佢地返工搵食<br />\n但佢地其實對勇武衝擊行為根本無感覺<br />\n即係你燒警署好、死警察好、打黑社會好<br />\n只要唔好搞到佢眼中正常生活就無問題<br />\n佢地唔會出黎阻撓個運動所以無必要再令佢地反感<br />\n<br />\n另外地區性集會一定要繼續做<br />\n好多平時只係靠TVb接觸資訊既人士<br />\n親眼係屋企樓下見到警察係幾離譜幾無禮貌<br />\n因為咁而轉向支持運動或反警陣營<br />\n佢地唔係100%運動支持者而係睇唔過眼警暴<br />\n反而一停一休息無左呢啲資訊接收就會變雨革2.0<br />\n當民眾慢慢淡出自然解散成場運動<br />\n8月5號既衝突鏡頭大眾根本都接受到<br />\n無必要一步退到去完全只靠和理非<br />\n應該轉型為Hit &amp; Run 不被捕地區衝突為主<br />\n<br />\n最後 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n徹底撤回逃犯條例<br />\n撤回運動任何暴動定性<br />\n必不追究反送中抗爭者<br />\n成立獨立委員會，徹查警方濫權濫暴及元朗暴力事件<br />\n全面落實雙真普選<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"e1b9e8a6f4b98b4c05b63d630c256837554c922e","tid":1434363,"uid":179402,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:06:33.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「幫幫手推一推」黑警唔單止搜身時恐嚇市民 仲要強光照市民對眼！ | LIHKG</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1434132/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1434132/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n原片：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/F74MRhonX28\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FF74MRhonX28&d=2tiv49EdsLtkS%2FsM0tMlCGINpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=76cee1fb\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/F74MRhonX28</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/OjM9aG3xZKk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FOjM9aG3xZKk&d=2tiv49EdsLtkS%2FsM0tMlCGINpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=7a273fa3\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/OjM9aG3xZKk</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">有乜野必要同理由對市民使用強光照住佢對眼？呢個行為有咩意義同對工作上有咩幫助？</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">強烈要求黑警回應點解要用惡劣 粗暴 令人不適嘅態度 語氣 行為 去對待配合黑警工作嘅市民！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n幫手派出去 推上報<br />\n<br />\n今次拍片者冇事 下個好難講<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a08da15c05064517e4b242b629a976a00d961a96","tid":1434363,"uid":5378,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:09:37.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"8f4e1797fe2b61390809bbb511ae1037bdd23646","tid":1434363,"uid":235465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:12:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f63842fbcd1aa86f90553de34eff689dfc38fc7","tid":1434363,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:18:10.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"515d3ca855d5b49b205eb95f8111edb38fc4ea6b","tid":1434363,"uid":273621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:18:59.000Z","msg":"想身邊人留意到可以考慮下<br />\n【升級方向】午餐？罷了<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1431510\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1431510</a>"},{"pid":"8244930bf69d204e3ce10ec1a6499f4164386318","tid":1434363,"uid":229411,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:19:52.000Z","msg":"同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7b222a7eb67499c78c4594655cec1cc9a5be443","tid":1434363,"uid":211317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:21:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b8f365a1354e74f05d8f61a458eadeeb6fbb9d45","tid":1434363,"uid":5378,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:22:34.000Z","msg":"有無人可以講下身邊真係有淺黃或中立覺得搞警局太暴力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我身邊連啲年長啲既同事都晚晚當戲睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 反而暫時未聽過有人覺得場面太暴力 就算放火或汽油彈 都係講左句 咁佢地抵死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a99aa7b4f0738dbbb8d1421b5022a0e122b73800","tid":1434363,"uid":260740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:28:25.000Z","msg":"我都注意到呢一點<br />\n所以會建議要塞都塞星期六、日<br />\n少D人返工...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n地鐵不合作運動仲做唔做？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1434022\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1434022</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2620c73a08f2816d29e68a29f87969fc2a4565a9","tid":1434363,"uid":5378,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a99aa7b4f0738dbbb8d1421b5022a0e122b73800","tid":1434363,"uid":260740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:28:25.000Z","msg":"我都注意到呢一點<br />\n所以會建議要塞都塞星期六、日<br />\n少D人返工...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n地鐵不合作運動仲做唔做？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1434022\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1434022</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:42:09.000Z","msg":"暫時睇唔到塞交通會吸到咩新支持者<br />\n反而有啲趕客feel"},{"pid":"699563123e87368985e6b5418d97aed70d02a298","tid":1434363,"uid":260740,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2620c73a08f2816d29e68a29f87969fc2a4565a9","tid":1434363,"uid":5378,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a99aa7b4f0738dbbb8d1421b5022a0e122b73800","tid":1434363,"uid":260740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:28:25.000Z","msg":"我都注意到呢一點<br />\n所以會建議要塞都塞星期六、日<br />\n少D人返工...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n地鐵不合作運動仲做唔做？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1434022\" data-auto-link target