34363,"uid":260740,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2620c73a08f2816d29e68a29f87969fc2a4565a9","tid":1434363,"uid":5378,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:42:09.000Z","msg":"暫時睇唔到塞交通會吸到咩新支持者<br />\n反而有啲趕客feel"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T19:09:06.000Z","msg":"Exactly....<br />\n有一啲事其實係要好多人有共識先至做得到<br />\n勉強只會帶來反效果"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T19:31:57.000Z","msg":"反而燒狗屋睇到啲中立𨶙食花生拍哂手掌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我諗香港人底線真係唔好搞出人命同搞到佢自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T20:40:05.000Z","msg":"冇錯<br />\n而且好重要嘅一點係<br />\n佢哋係對警察好反感<br />\n所以警察嗰啲佢哋唔介意（唔好搞到文物就得）<br />\n反而覺得佢哋deserve，因為到目前為止完全沒有任何機制可以懲罰到濫權失職嘅警察<br />\n但問題如果左到返工<br />\n咁即係搞到佢哋，而佢哋係無辜嘅<br />\n甚至係支持呢個運動<br />\n但就變成受害者<br />\n所以會好不滿甚至反感"},{"pid":"ee130ad6cfba14973e534d27943fcef6f3b059fd","tid":1434363,"uid":5378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T01:40:17.000Z","msg":"光復香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f60469bc7f75e61755ac45f9024edab7e2876df","tid":1434363,"uid":5378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:35:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b68d74384483454b0478a843677ebbd8a3a86a5","tid":1434363,"uid":5378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:30:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71a40d7743f89391f9cbbfd5abbeb9ba3f9e3290","tid":1434363,"uid":106252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:32:26.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c2f6b6e0be3bb44f10f5f1e51ecb433f3aba6e3","tid":1434363,"uid":207462,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:35:50.000Z","msg":"暫時聽得最多不滿85主要都係警察家屬/親戚<br />\n但呢堆人為數不少<br />\n可以嘅暫時唔好升級得咁快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f73bfe521d24b5891ee67e31c0bb91ccd839179","tid":1434363,"uid":199257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:37:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65b00f937bc736fd4ccbd50a946e44676114122f","tid":1434363,"uid":22046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:38:44.000Z","msg":"推 同意"},{"pid":"0d2e1c9ada483d79402b66920f917f1fc4fbec44","tid":1434363,"uid":286412,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:38:51.000Z","msg":"有冇人同我諗法一樣？我覺得政府依家可能需要一個落台階。如果一開始係和平，佢係唔會理你，但經過激烈衝突後其實佢都攰，可能想妥協，但面子問題佢一定唔會妥協，而且怕做成壞榜樣日後個個都以為用暴力就會令政府妥協，所以在暴力衝擊下決不會妥協。呢排靜左，不如大家再俾多次機會去證明政府會唔會接受和平訴求。如果再次和平示威遊行，政府仍然不理會，咁我就死心了，和理非收得皮，以後再冇藉口叫勇武用和平方式。"},{"pid":"af897e148a477fb62344b54ed3a429ec1b49d79e","tid":1434363,"uid":274655,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:39:23.000Z","msg":"又自己圍威喂  <br />\n對社會零影響<br />\n邊個會理你？"},{"pid":"e660d539d750aa0d57b0f8d490942f416e7ed375","tid":1434363,"uid":269221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:40:21.000Z","msg":"我無野講"}]}